,"body":"그럼 지금 바로 가지고 올 테니까 조금만 기다려!\n아코, 빨리 올 테니까 괜찮아.\n걱정하지 마?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event12-02-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"……하하.\n응, 그럼 잘 부탁해.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"event12-02-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"아코","body":"어디 보자, 물도 준비하고 약도 챙겨야지!\n또…… 아! 스포츠 드링크를 사 왔지!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event12-02-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"아코","body":"그리고 땀 닦을 타올도 가져가야지!\n빨리, 빨리~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event12-02-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"토모에","body":"「괜찮아. 걱정하지 마.」\n라……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"mo